This is the default [[sound sequence]] for opening a normal door without a particular texture in ''[[Strife]]''. It is redirected from [[DoorSmallMetal]]. It is also used for opening [[animated door]]s with the DORCRG01 texture.
==== [[SNDSEQ]] definition ==== :DoorOpenSmallMetal play doors/small_metal_open nostopcutoff end [[Category:Sound sequences]]
